          "canonical": "[ edit | edit source ]\n • Violet's Bane can be harvested in the entrance caves of all Deepmines Bounties .\n • May be awarded randomly as a bonus bounty reward at the end of the mission, appearing just beside the extraction elevator.\n\n• Can be purchased for 10 Fergolyte from Nightcap , requiring Rank 2 - Curious .\n\n | Location\n |\n | Mushroom |\n | Effect\n |\n\n | Deepmines Caves\n(Stage 1 zone in all bounties)\n |\n | Muck Bonnet\n |\n | Weapons inflict Toxin Damage.\n |\n\n | Reeking Puffball\n |\n | Weapons inflict Gas Damage. Player is surrounded by cloudy green effects.\n |\n\n | Dull Button\n |\n | Clears existing Mushroom effects.\n |\n\n | Violet's Bane\n |\n | Weapons inflict Viral Damage. Spawns four Clems that follow the player, but their gunfire will harmlessly phase through enemies.\n |",
